A hospital is being shut down after it allegedly injected fruit juice into someone's veins!
Some vow it was just “bad” platelets, but either way – The owner of the Indian hospital claims his employees are to blame – not him –  Because they were supposed to acquire the correct platelets. And now, the hospital’s probably gonna get bulldozed because an investigation also found it was “illegally constructed.”
